---
import DocsLayout from "../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";

const toc = [
    { id: "introduction", title: "Introduction", level: 2 },
    { id: "features", title: "Features", level: 2 },
    { id: "getting-started", title: "Getting Started", level: 2 },
];
---

<DocsLayout
    title="Introduction"
    description="Welcome to the documentation"
    toc={toc}
>
    <h1 class="scroll-m-20 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">Introduction</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mt-2">
        Welcome to our component documentation built with Astro, Vue, and
        shadcn-vue.
    </p>

    <section id="introduction" class="scroll-mt-20 mt-12">
        <h2
            class="font-heading scroll-m-20 border-b pb-2 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight"
        >
            What is this?
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-muted-foreground">
            This is a modern documentation system built with cutting-edge
            technologies to provide the best developer experience. It combines
            the performance of Astro with the reactivity of Vue and the
            beautiful components from shadcn-vue.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section id="features" class="scroll-mt-20 mt-12">
        <h2
            class="font-heading scroll-m-20 border-b pb-2 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight"
        >
            Features
        </h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground list-disc list-inside">
            <li>⚡ Lightning-fast performance with Astro</li>
            <li>🎨 Beautiful, customizable components with shadcn-vue</li>
            <li>📱 Fully responsive design</li>
            <li>🌙 Dark mode support</li>
            <li>📝 Easy to add new documentation pages</li>
            <li>💻 Syntax-highlighted code blocks</li>
            <li>🔍 Table of contents navigation</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="getting-started" class="scroll-mt-20 mt-12">
        <h2
            class="font-heading scroll-m-20 border-b pb-2 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight"
        >
            Getting Started
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-muted-foreground">
            Check out the <a
                href="/docs/components/sidebar"
                class="text-primary hover:underline">Sidebar component</a
            >
            to see a complete example of how to document a component.
        </p>
    </section>
</DocsLayout>
